SELECT S.ID, S.NAME FROM STUDENTS S WHERE S.DEPARTMENT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT D.ID FROM STUDENTS S JOIN DEPARTMENTS D ON S.DEPARTMENT_ID = D.ID )
SELECT S.ID,S.NAME FROM DEPARTMENTS D RIGHT JOIN STUDENTS S ON S.DEPARTMENT_ID = D.ID WHERE D.ID IS NULL
SELECT S.ID, S.NAME FROM STUDENTS AS S LEFT JOIN DEPARTMENTS AS D ON S.DEPARTMENT_ID = D.ID WHERE S.DEPARTMENT_ID NOT IN (SELECT ID FROM DEPARTMENTS) GROUP BY S.ID
SELECT ID, NAME FROM STUDENTS WHERE DEPARTMENT_ID NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT ID FROM DEPARTMENTS) ORDER BY ID
SELECT S.ID, S.NAME FROM STUDENTS S LEFT JOIN DEPARTMENTS D ON D.ID = S.DEPARTMENT_ID WHERE D.ID IS NULL ORDER BY S.ID ASC

WITH A AS ( SELECT DEPARTMENT_ID FROM STUDENTS WHERE DEPARTMENT_ID NOT IN (SELECT ID FROM DEPARTMENTS GROUP BY 1) GROUP BY 1 ) SELECT ID, NAME FROM A JOIN STUDENTS B ON A.DEPARTMENT_ID = B.DEPARTMENT_ID GROUP BY 1,2
SELECT S.NAME ,S.ID FROM STUDENTS S WHERE S.DEPARTMENT_ID NOT IN (SELECT ID FROM DEPARTMENTS )
SELECT S.ID, S.NAME FROM STUDENTS S WHERE DEPARTMENT_ID NOT IN (SELECT D.ID FROM DEPARTMENTS D)
SELECT ID, NAME FROM (SELECT S.ID AS ID, S.NAME AS NAME, D.ID AS DID FROM STUDENTS S LEFT JOIN DEPARTMENTS D ON D.ID = S.DEPARTMENT_ID) TEMP1 WHERE DID IS NULL
SELECT S.ID AS ID , S.NAME FROM STUDENTS S LEFT JOIN DEPARTMENTS D ON S.DEPARTMENT_ID = D.ID WHERE D.ID IS NULL

WITH CTE AS (SELECT DISTINCT DEPARTMENT_ID FROM STUDENTS S LEFT JOIN DEPARTMENTS D ON S.DEPARTMENT_ID= D.ID WHERE D.ID IS NULL) SELECT DISTINCT ID,NAME FROM STUDENTS WHERE DEPARTMENT_ID IN (SELECT DISTINCT DEPARTMENT_ID FROM CTE)

SELECT ID, NAME FROM STUDENTS LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT ID AS DEPARTMENT_ID, NAME AS DEPARTMENT_NAME FROM DEPARTMENTS) AS TEMP ON STUDENTS.DEPARTMENT_ID = TEMP.DEPARTMENT_ID WHERE DEPARTMENT_NAME IS NULL
SELECT DISTINCT STUDENTS.ID AS ID, STUDENTS.NAME AS NAME FROM STUDENTS LEFT JOIN DEPARTMENTS ON STUDENTS.DEPARTMENT_ID = DEPARTMENTS.ID WHERE DEPARTMENTS.NAME IS NULL
SELECT T2.ID, T2.NAME FROM (SELECT STUDENTS.ID, STUDENTS.NAME, D.ID AS DID FROM STUDENTS LEFT OUTER JOIN DEPARTMENTS AS D ON STUDENTS.DEPARTMENT_ID = D.ID) AS T2 WHERE T2.DID IS NULL

SELECT S_ID AS ID,S_NAME AS NAME FROM(SELECT S.ID AS S_ID,S.NAME AS S_NAME,S.DEPARTMENT_ID AS S_DID,D.NAME AS D_NAME FROM STUDENTS S LEFT JOIN DEPARTMENTS D ON S.DEPARTMENT_ID = D.ID WHERE D.NAME IS NULL)FHFH

SELECT ID, NAME FROM (SELECT STUDENTS.ID AS ID, STUDENTS.NAME AS NAME, DEPARTMENTS.NAME AS DEPTNAME FROM STUDENTS LEFT JOIN DEPARTMENTS ON DEPARTMENTS.ID = STUDENTS.DEPARTMENT_ID) A WHERE DEPTNAME IS NULL
SELECT ID, NAME FROM STUDENTS S WHERE NOT EXISTS ( SELECT 1 FROM DEPARTMENTS D WHERE S.DEPARTMENT_ID = D.ID )

WITH CTE AS(SELECT S.DEPARTMENT_ID FROM STUDENTS S LEFT JOIN DEPARTMENTS D ON S.DEPARTMENT_ID=D.ID WHERE D.NAME IS NULL) SELECT DISTINCT S.ID,S.NAME FROM STUDENTS S JOIN CTE ON S.DEPARTMENT_ID=CTE.DEPARTMENT_ID
SELECT S.ID, S.NAME FROM STUDENTS S WHERE NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM DEPARTMENTS D WHERE S.DEPARTMENT_ID = D.ID)
SELECT DISTINCT A.ID, A.NAME FROM STUDENTS A LEFT JOIN DEPARTMENTS B ON A.DEPARTMENT_ID = B.ID WHERE B.ID IS NULL
SELECT STUDENTS.ID, STUDENTS.NAME FROM DEPARTMENTS RIGHT JOIN STUDENTS ON DEPARTMENTS.ID=STUDENTS.DEPARTMENT_ID WHERE DEPARTMENT_ID NOT IN (SELECT ID FROM DEPARTMENTS)
WITH T1 AS (SELECT S.ID AS ID, S.NAME AS NAME, D.NAME AS DEP_NAME FROM STUDENTS AS S LEFT JOIN DEPARTMENTS AS D ON S.DEPARTMENT_ID = D.ID) SELECT ID, NAME FROM T1 WHERE DEP_NAME IS NULL
SELECT DISTINCT ID,NAME FROM STUDENTS WHERE DEPARTMENT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT DISTINCT ID FROM DEPARTMENTS)
SELECT ID,NAME FROM STUDENTS S WHERE ID NOT IN ( SELECT S.ID AS ID FROM STUDENTS S JOIN DEPARTMENTS D ON S.DEPARTMENT_ID=D.ID)
SELECT S.ID AS ID, S.NAME AS NAME FROM STUDENTS S WHERE S.DEPARTMENT_ID NOT IN (SELECT D.ID FROM DEPARTMENTS D)
SELECT S.ID, S.NAME FROM STUDENTS S WHERE NOT EXISTS (SELECT * FROM DEPARTMENTS D WHERE D.ID=S.DEPARTMENT_ID)
SELECT STUDENTS.ID, STUDENTS.NAME FROM STUDENTS WHERE DEPARTMENT_ID NOT IN (SELECT DEPARTMENTS.ID FROM DEPARTMENTS)

SELECT A.ID,A.NAME FROM ( SELECT STUDENTS.ID,STUDENTS.NAME,STUDENTS.DEPARTMENT_ID,DEPARTMENTS.ID AS DEP_ID FROM STUDENTS LEFT JOIN DEPARTMENTS ON STUDENTS.DEPARTMENT_ID=DEPARTMENTS.ID)AS A WHERE A.DEP_ID IS NULL
SELECT S.ID, S.NAME FROM STUDENTS S WHERE S.DEPARTMENT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT D.ID FROM STUDENTS S INNER JOIN DEPARTMENTS D ON S.DEPARTMENT_ID = D.ID )
